      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tee peoerterru Ancosta\nBehrnu Behrneem / pehz tahm\nKaiitiru Saimehm no Lewja\nBehrneem/ jo ta ptrina Mesflo-\nschanas Teesa peedetreja win-\nneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee dewe teem to Pils-\nfahrtu Kiriat-Arbu / ta Eenaka\nTehwa/fcis irr Eebroṅs us Inh-\nda Kalneem/un winna Preekſch-\nPilſtahtu apkahrt winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ta Pilſtahta Tihru-\nnu / un winna Zeemus dewe tee\nRahlebam Jewuka Dehſam var\nJhpafchunu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta dewe tee Aāroṇa ta\nPreestera Behrneemi tohs Gelbe-\nschanas-Pilsfahrtu preekſch No-\nkaweja / Eebroṅu un winna\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ/un Libnu un\nwinnas Preekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jatiru / un winna\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ / un Eṣ-\nmon / un winna Preekſch-Pils-\nfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Oloṇu / un winna\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ/un Debiru/\nun winna Preekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ainu / un winnas\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ / un Juhtu/\nun winnas Preekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ/\nun Bet - Seemi / un winnas\nPreekſch - Pilsfahrtuṣ / dewin\nPilsfahrtu no schahm dtiwizultim-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Benjaminā Zilts\nGibeonu / un winna Preekſch-\nPilsfahrtuṣ / Gebu / un winna\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Anatotu / un winna\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ / un Almo-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pilsfahti Aāroṇ\nta Preestera Dehlu bija trihsp-\ndefinitis Pilsfahti / ar fanwee\nPreekſch-Pilsfahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tahm Saimehm\nKaiita Behrnu / to Lewttu / ka-\nattikufchi bija no teem Kaiā\nBehrneem / tikke tee Pilsfah-\nwinnu Mesfloshanas no tahs G\nwrāima Zilts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee dewe teem Sikem-\nweenu Gelbefchannas - Pilsfahrt-\npreekſch Nokaweja / un win-\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ/ us Getwā-\nma Kalnu/ un Geseru/ un win-\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ribzāim / un win-\nPreekſch - Pilsfahrtuṣ / un Be-\nOronu/un winna Preekſch-Pil-\nfahrtuṣ / tschetr Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Danna Zilts Elt-\nku / un winna Preekſch-Pilsfa-\ntuṣ / un Gibetonu / un win-\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ajalonu / un win-\nPreekſch-Pilsfahrtuṣ / Gat-Ri-\nmonu/ un winna Preekſch-Pil-\nfahrtuṣ / tschetr Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un no Manaffus pu-\nZilts Taenakā/un winna Preekſch-\nPilsfahrtuṣ / un Gat-Rimonu-\nnu winna Preekſch-Pilsfahrtu-\ndiwiz Pilsfahrtuṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſi Pilsfahti preekſ-\ntahmSaimehm to attikufschuR-\nata Behrnu irr deymits ar fanwee\nPreekſch-Pilsfahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un teem Gersona Beh-\nnee\n"
    }
  ],
